        "h3": { "en": "Motor A", "zh": "电机 A" },
        "body": { "en": "We refer to the left motor as Motor A.", "zh": "我们把左边的电机叫电机 A。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:110mm; top:30mm; width:80mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Note the wire direction", "zh": "注意引线朝向" },
        "body": { "en": "Confirm the motor's wires face the direction shown before fixing the bracket.", "zh": "固定支架前，先确认电机引线的朝向和图里一致。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:110mm; top:60mm; width:80mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Leave the bolts loose", "zh": "螺栓先别拧紧" },
        "body": { "en": "Don't fully tighten the motor mount yet — you'll slide it later to tension the belt.", "zh": "电机座先别完全拧紧——后面还要靠滑动它来张紧同步带。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:150mm; top:128mm; width:80mm;"
      }
    ]
  },
