        "h3": { "en": "Mirror", "zh": "镜像" },
        "body": { "en": "This is the right motor — mirror of the left. The cable connector faces right.", "zh": "这是右边的电机——和左边的左右对称，线缆接头朝右。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:120mm; width:78mm;"
